The family of Bongekile Simelane, better known as Babes Wodumo, held a press conference after a video showing her being assaulted by her boyfriend Mandla Maphumulo went viral. DURBAN - The family of Bongekile Simelane, better known as Babes Wodumo, held a press conference after a video showing her being assaulted by her boyfriend went viral. Wodumo on Monday opened a case of assault against Mandla Maphumulo, who is also known as Mampintsha, at the Westville Police Station in Durban. WATCH: Babes Wodumo media briefing 